Change: Move file name deduplication from SharedMount contructor to View class

The deduplication of shared filenames is being done in the SharedMount constructor,
accesing the filesystem constantly, and hiting the performance as more files are
shared.

I just move code around to achieve the same result.

https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/38427
https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/38063